lead_paragraph: The head of a Tokyo government cost-cutting panel has criticized 2020 Olympic organizers for not cooperating on recommendations designed to reduce spiraling expenses for the games.

headline.print_headline: Tokyo Panel Head Says 2020 Organizers Not Cooperating
